        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nSubsequent verifies fail when an add of a submodule does not include both a valid gitmodules entry AND a corresponding directory under submodules. This patch set adds the partial update that was backed out to maintain stability of master preparing for Amsterdam branch.  https://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/23803/.  The steps to insure both of these occur together are described here http://docs.onap.org/en/amsterdam/guides/onap-developer/how-to-use-docs/include-documentation.html#setup-project-repositories-s",
        "patchset_number": 1
